data.description: This Is A Lovely Ranch Type Home On 70 Level Acres With 1/4 Mi Frontage On Pyramid Hwy. Home Sits To The Back of Property For Privacy. The Acreage Used To Be In Cultivation In The Past. It Is A Rural Oasis On The Way To Pyramid Lake. The Property Has Two Wells On The Property A Domestic Well, And An Irrigation Well.Bring Your Buyers Who Want A Great Rural Getaway With Excellent Access And Potential.
